# SA_loop_seed_cycle — 씨앗 생성 + 검증 + 전달 전 사이클

> L2 Composed | 구성: think_fuse → act_create_seed → loop_review → act_send_mail
> 용도: 융합 결과에서 씨앗 생성 → NAEL Gate 검증 → 승인 시 멤버에게 전달
> 비용: high

## PPR

```python
def SA_loop_seed_cycle():
    intel = SA_think_fuse()

    if not intel["fusions"]:
        return {"status": "no_fusions", "seeds": 0}

    seed = SA_act_create_seed(intel["fusions"], intel["patterns"])

    verdict, reviews = SA_loop_review(seed, reviewers={
        "NAEL": {"file": "NAEL.md", "lens": "보안·안전"},
        "Vera": {"file": "Vera.md", "lens": "데이터 품질·현실 정렬"},
    })

    if verdict == "APPROVED":
        target = AI_identify_target_members(seed)
        for member in target:
            SA_act_send_mail(member, "seed", seed.summary)
        SA_act_notify("toast", "씨앗 전달", f"{seed.id} → {target}")
    elif verdict == "BLOCKED":
        SA_act_notify("alert", "씨앗 BLOCKED", f"{seed.id}: {reviews}")

    return {"status": verdict, "seed": seed.id}
```
